# description
List of diff and merge tools

# diff tools
vimdiff
gvimdiff - almost identical to vimdiff but uses Linux GUI for Vim, refer to vimdiff
nvimdiff
opendiff
diffoscope
meld
xxdiff - requires x11
kdiff3 - KDE ?
kompare - KDE ?
meld

# windows only?
tortoisemerge
